 
& addsp3
 
  
  Example:
  To add a Targeting Computer to the RS Unit in the left torso at 
  critslot 1
  
  >addsp targetingcomputer lt 1 
  Critical slot filled.
  
  >critstatus lt
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                             Left Torso Criticals                             
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1 TargetingComputer                    7 Empty                               
 2 Empty                                8 Empty                               
 3 Empty                                9 Empty                               
 4 Empty                               10 Empty                               
 5 Empty                               11 Empty                               
 6 Empty                               12 Empty                               
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 
  See Also: attarget
 